          <div class="card-product-infos">
            <h2>Company (Cost 450)</h2>
            <p>Create a company! A whole team coding just for you. They love casual Fridays at the office.</p>
          </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card-product" id="big-tech" data-action="click->code-computer#hireBigTech">
          <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dgqqot40q/image/upload/w_1000,ar_1:1,c_fill,g_auto,e_art:hokusai/v1688380161/Screenshot_2023-07-03_at_11.23.33_lw0j4e.png" />
          <div class="card-product-infos">
            <h2>Big Tech (Cost 1,350)</h2>
            <p>Create a Big Tech! Dominate the market and monopolize all the coding of the world.</p>
          </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card-product" id="quantum-computer" data-action="click->code-computer#hireQuantumComputer">
          <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dgqqot40q/image/upload/v1689681658/EDxIonhUEAI9Tz8_ta2zvd.jpg" />
          <div class="card-product-infos">
            <h2>Quantum Computer (Cost 5,000)</h2>
            <p>Build a Quantum Computer! This bad boys can code to horizons never seen before.</p>
          </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card-product" id="AI" data-action="click->code-computer#hireAi">
          <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dgqqot40q/image/upload/v1688380978/Screenshot_2023-07-03_at_11.40.58_q1ekk3.png" />
          <div class="card-product-infos">
            <h2>AI (Cost 20,000)</h2>
            <p>Build an Artificial Intelligence! In the limit between machine and man they will code things above your understanding.</p>
          </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card-product" id="coding-star" data-action="click->code-computer#hireCodingStar">
          <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dgqqot40q/image/upload/v1688381695/code-star_rhmuof.png" />
          <div class="card-product-infos">
            <h2>Coding Star (Cost 100,000)</h2>
            <p>Construct a Coding Star! Go beyond and create a space station that will code unimaginable things.</p>
          </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card-product" id="architect" data-action="click->code-computer#hireArchitect">
          <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dgqqot40q/image/upload/v1688380308/architect_z2rev3.webp" />
          <div class="card-product-infos">
            <h2>The Architect (Cost 500,000)</h2>
            <p>Creator of reality as we know the Architect can code anything into existence.</p>
          </div>
          </div>

      </div>
  </div>

</div>
